# Workflow Engine — Bunyan

## Overview

The workflow engine manages construction project lifecycle:
Project → Phases → Tasks → Reports

## Status Flow

Pending → In Progress → Complete → Paid

## Configuration

- Global config stored in database
- Per-project overrides as JSON or separate rows
- Resolution: per-project override > global default
- Config changes audited

## Rules

- Status transitions validated server-side against workflow configuration
- Approval workflows with role-based approval gates
- Field engineer reporting frequency rules (daily, every X days, weekly)
- Configuration snapshots at project creation
- Per-project overrides loaded before global defaults

